{"tid":1401911,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我宣布新形抗爭方式-和理非之盾！！！！！勇武之矛！！！！！！","createTime":"2019-08-03T15:20:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T16:08:57.000Z","uid":76558,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c37305ede55f7dd9c30e82dd4d18b6e5ae81d00f","tid":1401911,"uid":76558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:20:38.000Z","msg":"經過左旺角今晚ge 情況，我相信好多手足已經要明白<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">hit&amp;run</span></span></strong>ge重要性，死守打陣地已經唔入流，只會做成前線手足被速狗不斷咬，以下將會講解新形抗爭手法<br />\n<br />\n前線勇務：<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Hit &amp; run</span></span></strong><br />\n響前線ge 手足set 整好路障之後， 你地火法中意用魔攻又好落石術又好，無任歡迎。但當見到狗上晒裝， 堆好防線， 呢個時候就要開始提高警覺！！！  要留意好逃走路線，盡量保持鬆動空間，以空間換取優勢，只有跑動，先可以贏到速龍！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n和理非：<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">決定成敗的關鍵因素</span></span></strong>, <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">成為勇武的盾牌</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我知大家做得和理非，有負擔唔上得前線， 咁作為後排有咩用？  新形戰術强調要run, 但run ge前題係需要有一條安全路線。 呢個時候請各位和理非化身開路先鋒。 <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記住</span></span></strong>我地<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔係</span></span>佔路，我地係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">和平散去</span></span>,我地散唔一定係入地鐵站走，今晚旺角散去九龍城，上次中環修頓散落去西環中聯辦。就算d警察黎到！！！ 大家只要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">上番行人路</span></span>  就無事！！！！<br />\n<br />\n只要開到路，我地就可以永續遊行！繼承左前線唔想俾人咁易清場ge理念，亦俾到機會 和理非參加百萬行ge欲望。<br />\n<br />\n當然呢個戰術要避免俾狗4面圍堵，所以有賴各位連軍師 繼續改善！<br />\n<br />\n祝各位<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">武運昌隆</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">光復香港</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"c333f33046a46863b270c1d1dcc77f7396724ee2","tid":1401911,"uid":76558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:21:39.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"449cbefe5e56a29cdefc9e156c1ad4275c9ff4f5","tid":1401911,"uid":284951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:22:26.000Z","msg":"不分化 不割蓆 不指責<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"c9c6a64974593c2a873b7800b4aa51d3781b773c","tid":1401911,"uid":76558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:22:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"600a36c6a7d29d65129b293027e0393d4c931c3b","tid":1401911,"uid":76558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:24:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />1"},{"pid":"1c842a399cc1497c435e59dea8f779ce8137cfac","tid":1401911,"uid":76558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:25:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />2"},{"pid":"43ed727ba4fa3edad893752ae6a72a32408e9c22","tid":1401911,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:31:48.000Z","msg":"不留守，不被捕"},{"pid":"6f8a581a57027849de83998502e7279e835731b5","tid":1401911,"uid":25169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:32:35.000Z","msg":"[建議]關於罷買！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1401281\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1401281</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8d1d2592a50dc8eb4c82038772eb99ae4115f92f","tid":1401911,"uid":267235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:34:56.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 借位推post<br />\n<br />\n[和理非大集合] 8.5 唔返工，我哋全港遊車河<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1401887\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1401887</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"461c3767e3083a8bf7f67c26364f390b25f94413","tid":1401911,"uid